     There is a wide variety of scientific meetings, conferences, and
     training sessions relevant to symptom research. The following Web sites
     provide information concerning those meetings.

     Academy for Health Services Research and Policy
     Annual Meeting
     June 10 -12
     Atlanta, Georgia
     http://academyhealth.org/2001/index.htm

     American Academy of Hospice and Palliative Medicine (AAHPM)
     13th Annual Assembly of the AAHPM
     June 21 - 24, 2001
     Pointe Hilton Squaw Peak Resort, Phoenix, Arizona
     http://www.aahpm.org/events.htm
